This project is a test project that using ant to compile, test, etc.

Please make sure you install Apache ant first.
- How to Install Apache Ant: https://youtu.be/kEqv1PoOFc4

Other references:
- Ant core concept: https://youtu.be/8MhYLrtf_zY

Basically, this test project is following ant manual https://ant.apache.org/manual/index.html.

To import external libraries like log4j library to intellij, follow below steps:
1. download the lib jar;
2. move it to project libs/
3. right click the jar file, and click 'Add to libraries'

Run:

ant

or

ant clean test